      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAVENDER LANE (2) looks close to another win after hitting the frame in a 6 length second (20.15) in a Other at this track. Must come into calculations. LIFE OF RILEY (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 3.5 lengths second (23.28) over 400m at Gawler. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in six starts. Can measure up. CATCH MY DESIGN (7) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a neck (16.99) behind Toledo at Murray Bridge. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Expecting another good run. AILEEN'S SHINE (8) will have admirers after placing last time out.",
